org.ggp.base.player.gamer

Class Gamer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ggp.base.player.gamer.Gamer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Subject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClojureGamer, PythonGamer, StateMachineGamer

    public abstract class Gamer
extends java.lang.Object
implements Subject
    The Gamer class defines methods for both meta-gaming and move selection in a pre-specified amount of time. The Gamer class is based on the algorithm design pattern.
